message.entry: Input matrix must be double or logical.
Input matrix must be double, single, or logical.
''{0}'' value must be a real numeric scalar.
Incorrect number of input arguments. Each parameter name must be followed by a corresponding value.
''MaxImbalance'' value must be an integer multiple of 0.001 between 1.001 and 1.999, inclusive.
''MaxDegreeThreshold'' value must be a nonnegative integer.
''NumIterations'' value must be an integer greater than or equal to 1.
''NumSeparators'' value must be an integer greater than or equal to 1.
''VertexWeights'' value must be a real vector the same length as the number of rows of the input matrix.
''VertexWeights'' value must be a vector of integers greater than or equal to 1.
